{"type": "article", "id": 27814, "title": "柠檬榨汁器", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-06T06:57:53Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702110512nDaZPCkG6AFxKm3s.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>到了夏天，柠檬的出场机会也越来越多。传统的柠檬榨汁器虽然好用，但往往你还是得亲手把最后那几滴汁水挤出来——如果你前几天不小心弄伤了手指，这可是件比较头疼的事。Nicasio Priolo 设计的这款名为 Lemon Drop 的榨汁器看上去很像一个钻地机，可以根据果肉的分割线深入柠檬内部将汁水挤出。这样一来，你就不用担心手上沾满柠檬汁了。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070211051042A1YLx6IUgEyTPm.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021105115HytAkIijGJbBqd2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75904762\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110511lJwGqHjsDRnOvYMk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}